main event: Civilian observers reported seeing a large, silent object illuminating the area like an airborne searchlight in Cisco, Texas on August 14, 1966.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 10 minutes before moving out of sight to the northwest., The sighting occurred at a low altitude of about 1000 feet., Witnesses noted that the object had lights along its edges which blinked brightly., Similar sightings were reported by other observers in the area at the same time., The reporting observer was left both amazed and scared by the sighting.
sighted object: a large, saucer-shaped object emitting bright lights
witness description: civilian observers including a college student
